C o m p a r a t i v e n o t e s: The combination of characters as structure of antennae, stalked eyes, shape of pronotum and of median thoracic ridge and structure and position of male glandular tubercle on vltg VII is not shared by any other apterous neotropical 
Aradidae
(KORMILEV & FROESCHNER, 1987; COSCARON & CONTRERAS, 2012; PANIZZI & GRAZIA, 2015; 
HEISS 2018
).
